Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:08.23,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Mr. Rizzo that the chef here is quite talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.18,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:16.83,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,This is tonight's antipasto misto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.72,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time to savor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:30.53,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,See? It looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:31.64,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:51.86,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:53.88,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:54.53,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Waiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:55.89,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:03.15,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Why do all the employees here wear spectacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:06.04,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's this restaurant's trademark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:06.96,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:14.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,This mysterious restaurant is on a road just a little ways from the center of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.09,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:59.44,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those are photographs taken when this restaurant opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.75,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,The staff has changed a little since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.54,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That man wasn't wearing spectacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.66,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's why he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.58,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, he was fired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:13.61,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. That's not grounds for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.57,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But the owner is a curious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:20.49,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,It's one thing to have a wife who likes bespectacled gentlemen, it's another to open a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:25.21,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, this wine is truly delectable, Gigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:29.82,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,He treats his wife like a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.43,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,She truly met a wonderful man to make her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.93,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her, smiling like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.00,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.31,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:42.62,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to speak your mind about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:47.95,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a friend of the Madam, you're a friend of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.64,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I will do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:58.52,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Man... Now I can't tell them I'm really her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:03.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's really comfortable living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:06.21,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking care of all my living expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:10.22,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Though she did break her promise to meet and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:13.28,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she is really busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:19.92,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Grandma... There's a guy I really like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:23.67,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't tell if it's love or what...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:27.73,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really good at talking about these sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.40,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you talk to Olga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:34.25,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She's your mother, plus you're all the way there, in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.80,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother was the one who suggested I go to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:46.46,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's because she wanted me to make up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:49.84,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I get that she's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:53.15,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I'm staying here in Rome,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.68,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I should probably look for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:06.25,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But, what sort of job should I look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:09.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I just moved here without thinking things through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.12,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,They're closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.37,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:33.11,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go get some food, Francesco?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.48,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.39,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,How about that panini place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.89,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they have my usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:40.89,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:42.55,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.19,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:52.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.20,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Luciano!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:01.22,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nonno, who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.59,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,She's a friend of the owner's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:08.12,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, she's been coming to eat with the staff every day at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:11.63,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.88,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Francesco.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.38,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.34,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.28,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Don't believe everything your grandfather says about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.85,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.90,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Gigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.74,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Buon giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.75,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Are you always on this bench?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:41.91,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... Why can't they just let me relax on my day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.18,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Put that all in, too. We'll add in salt and pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.33,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at cooking, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:07:00.17,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I used to help my grandma cook since I was about your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.68,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandma? Not your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:06.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I learned how to cook from my grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.09,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:14.66,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Buono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.69,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Change your mind about me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:20.24,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, for an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.49,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:22.83,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:25.49,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.46,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Planning to stay in Rome forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.87,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What do your parents say about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:37.45,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,My daddy's always taking business trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.97,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:42.80,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, look for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.89,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just be here for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.47,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to take it seriously-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.48,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Save the speech, I'm already looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:50.73,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.51,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Don't copy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.51,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Don't copy her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.86,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:01.82,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Claudio's not coming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:10.30,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, since it's his day off, he's treating his wife and kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.21,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.38,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.88,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this pasta is actually edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:21.73,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:27.87,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like Nicoletta is spending a lot of time at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:32.40,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what to expect from her. She's still a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you invite her over sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.40,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's your friend and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:41.26,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't know how to connect to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:45.91,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,In my mind, she's still that little girl I knew years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.82,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Just treat her normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.33,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry so much. It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.26,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.46,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What's with Luciano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:06.04,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He treats me like a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:14.19,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's true, I've never really thought about my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:22.39,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I really should think about my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:28.03,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But, for the time being, love is just as important!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:32.49,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Buon giorno, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:33.87,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Buon giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:35.68,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Buon giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.12,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Is this love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.67,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.39,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:51.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Like this Luciano guy who does nothing but complain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:55.98,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:05.24,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,If he suddenly became really kind to me, would I fall in love with him over that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.60,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,They said it wasn't gonna rain today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.80,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I call you a cab?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.61,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine if I run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:23.08,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be fine doing that, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:27.11,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Use it. You'll both fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.72,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.89,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Luciano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.72,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm loaning it to Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:36.93,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Now take her home before the sky really opens up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.73,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:44.04,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:53.61,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. Gigi is somewhat strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.70,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,But he's a good guy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.53,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What's your wife like, Claudio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.39,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have one, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:19.39,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But... that ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:22.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason I wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:28.43,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,There are some customers who try and pursue me for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.72,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,They'll start talking about marriage and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is a countermeasure against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:38.41,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,My wife and I separated years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:42.92,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:46.60,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He opened up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.11,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the whole idea of adultery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:10.00,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never bring up the idea of marriage, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.33,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,My wife and I separated years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:27.84,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,There are some customers who try and pursue me for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:31.67,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is a countermeasure against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:36.77,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.85,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.92,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:42.92,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.27,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.43,Ristorante,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:52.28,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,This smells lovely. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.88,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I bought it at a shop nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.73,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.27,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.29,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take my eyes off of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:09.49,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,He's so much older than I am... I've never felt like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:22.23,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:26.52,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try and see if this is all right or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:33.16,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I know I like you, but I can't tell if it's real...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.84,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:42.68,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:45.66,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:56.72,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I think... he's a real gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:00.10,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Nicoletta, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.03,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you some chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:10.02,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your hands off my Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.77,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:15.03,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,All the gentlemen there belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:20.37,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry for being in your friend's apartment at such a late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.70,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.67,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I know that she dragged you here against your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.29,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.29,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let the two of you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.30,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You're not serious, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.45,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.30,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm single, so who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.64,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Then why not go after Luciano? He's single!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:49.81,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.50,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Teo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:55.32,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's like you don't want me going after Claudio for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:15:02.01,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I understand, but Claudio doesn't know how to handle a woman's advances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:05.33,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why don't you move back to your grandmother's?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.14,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:10.63,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You're young. There's no need to rush things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:13.91,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,You should focus on getting a job, and your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:18.22,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Why does everyone treat me like a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:19.22,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:21.18,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about all that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.79,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what I should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.90,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'd be good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:29.26,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at cooking, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:37.45,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why'd you go quiet all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.74,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:40.57,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:46.34,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,If you help me out, I'll reconsider telling your husband that I'm your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:58.18,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nicoletta and I'll be working as an apprentice here, starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.68,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.73,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Since Lorenzo said it was fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.31,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,it's OK with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:07.52,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But promise me you won't leave the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.59,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:19.68,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,So you've always had an interest in cooking, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.34,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,They said you even went to cooking school for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:27.08,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I had never thought about it as a career.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:30.08,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,So what made you change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:32.71,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't figure out what I wanted to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.58,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,but I knew I wanted to be independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:39.09,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on using this opportunity to learn everything I can about cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.59,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:43.88,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you give cooking classes at your home, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.86,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Can I join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.51,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:50.55,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Man, there's no pancetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.48,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Giuseppe swore up and down he'd get it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:58.07,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good. We can call, but it takes them a while to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.48,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,How about I go and get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.96,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.69,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Claudio. You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.54,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Please escort her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:24.84,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.94,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about last night, for doing that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.20,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,But, I want to let you know that I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.52,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:44.03,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I'll lay off a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:46.82,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nicoletta, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:49.84,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious about learning how to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:55.04,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't start working at the restaurant just because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:59.23,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try and pursue something I may be good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:01.37,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to always depend on Olga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:05.05,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be truly independent someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:09.51,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll become a great woman, and get back at {\i1}her{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:13.16,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of people treating me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:17.06,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Please give it your all. I'll support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:20.06,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I can use your support more than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.61,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:28.65,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:36.34,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,It's so great to be working in the same place as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:39.96,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gabrielle's coming tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.59,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make a really grand dolce, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:47.13,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Gabrielle? Could that be someone special?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.90,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.30,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Gabrielle is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.40,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:06.70,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is Gabrielle a VIP or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.70,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She's Claudio's ex-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.00,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.62,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:23.39,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She has such beautiful skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.21,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,That's his ex-wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:27.30,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:31.23,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is his "ex"-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.20,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.32,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:53.31,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to stop wearing that ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.46,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I won't order you to do it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.96,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:20.63,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I interrupted your conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:21.84,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.05,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Claudio...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:32.80,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Could he still have feelings for his ex-wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:42.84,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,The restaurant is located on a street in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:46.15,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is casetta dell'orso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:55.89,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,She's my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.85,Ristorante,FV,0000,0000,0000,,I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:00.89,Ristorante,MV,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
